{
  "openapi": "3.0.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "Cyber Media Center API (赛博影视)",
    "description": "## 专业发烧级影视中心后端接口文档\n\n此文档定义了 Cyber Media 的核心 API 交互规范。旨在取代 Plex/Emby，提供高性能、低延迟的媒体管理与流媒体服务。\n\n### 🔗 API 生命周期说明 (x-lifecycle-status)\n我们在每个接口中定义了开发状态，请前端同学注意：\n\n1.  🔴 **pending** (未开发): 接口仅有定义，后端尚未实现，调用会返回 501。\n2.  🟠 **implemented_unverified** (已开发未验证): 代码已合并，但未经完整测试，可能存在 Bug。\n3.  ❌ **failed_verification** (验证失败): 测试发现严重问题，暂时禁止使用。\n4.  ⚠️ **passed_imperfect** (验证通过但格式不规范): 功能可用，但返回字段可能不全或命名不符合规范，后续会变动。\n5.  ✅ **stable** (验证通过): 接口稳定，可放心集成。\n\n### 🛡️ 鉴权说明\n所有非公开接口需在 Header 中携带 `Authorization: Bearer <token>`。",
    "version": "1.9.4-beta",
    "contact": {
      "name": "Cyber Media Core Team",
      "email": "dev@cybermedia.local"
    }
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "https://alist.gameuniverse.top",
      "description": "生产环境 (Production)"
    },
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:5001",
      "description": "本地开发环境"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "✅ [验证通过] 健康检查",
        "description": "检查后端服务连通性及数据库连接状态。",
        "operationId": "healthCheck",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "stable",
        "tags": [
          "System"
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "服务正常",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "code": 200,
                  "msg": "Pong",
                  "data": {
                    "status": "up",
                    "version": "1.9.4"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/scan": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "✅ [验证通过] 获取扫描状态",
        "description": "轮询接口，用于获取当前扫描任务的实时进度。",
        "operationId": "getScanStatus",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "stable",
        "tags": [
          "System"
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "当前状态",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ScanStatus"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "post": {
        "summary": "✅ [验证通过] 触发媒体库扫描",
        "description": "异步触发全量或增量扫描。任务 ID 将在响应中返回，用于通过 WebSocket 监听进度。",
        "operationId": "triggerScan",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "stable",
        "tags": [
          "System"
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "type": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "enum": [
                      "full",
                      "incremental"
                    ],
                    "default": "incremental"
                  },
                  "target_path": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "指定扫描路径，留空则扫描全库"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "202": {
            "description": "任务已接受",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "429": {
            "description": "已有扫描任务正在运行"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/filters": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "🔵 [新增] 获取全局筛选字典",
        "description": "统一获取侧边栏筛选菜单所需的所有元数据（分类、年份、国家等）。替代了之前零散的 genre/year/region 接口，提高前端加载效率。",
        "operationId": "getGlobalFilters",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "stable",
        "tags": [
          "Library"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "include",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "可选：指定需要获取的筛选维度。如果为空，则返回所有。例如：'genres,years'",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "筛选字典",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/FilterDictionaries"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/movies": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "✅ [验证通过] 获取电影列表 (全能筛选)",
        "description": "获取电影库数据。支持多维度复合筛选：年份、地区、分类、关键词。",
        "operationId": "listMovies",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "stable",
        "tags": [
          "Library"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "page",
            "in": "query",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "default": 1
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "page_size",
            "in": "query",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "default": 20
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "keyword",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "搜索关键词",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "genre",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "分类筛选 (例如 'Action')。",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "country",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "地区/国家代码筛选 (例如 'US', 'CN', 'JP')。",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "year",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "年份筛选。支持单年份 '2023' 或范围 '2020-2024'。",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "source_id",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "存储源筛选",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "sort_by",
            "in": "query",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "date_added",
                "year",
                "rating",
                "title"
              ],
              "default": "date_added"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "order",
            "in": "query",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "asc",
                "desc"
              ],
              "default": "desc"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功返回分页数据",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "items": {
                              "type": "array",
                              "items": {
                                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/MovieSimple"
                              }
                            },
                            "pagination": {
                              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PaginationMeta"
                            }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/movies/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "🟠 [已开发未验证] 获取电影详情",
        "description": "获取单部电影的完整元数据。",
        "operationId": "getMovieDetail",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "Library"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "电影的唯一 UUID",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "详情数据",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/MovieDetailed"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "404": {
            "description": "未找到该电影"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/movies/{id}/fix_match": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "🔵 [新增] 手动修正匹配 (Fix Match)",
        "description": "当自动刮削错误时，用户可手动提供 TMDB ID，后端将重新下载元数据并覆盖当前电影信息。",
        "operationId": "fixMovieMatch",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "Library"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "电影的唯一 UUID",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "tmdb_id"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "tmdb_id": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "正确的 TMDB ID"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "修正任务已提交",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/resources/{id}/stream": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "⚠️ [格式不规范] 视频流媒体",
        "description": "直接返回二进制视频流。",
        "operationId": "streamVideo",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "passed_imperfect",
        "tags": [
          "Player"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "container",
            "in": "query",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "hls",
                "mp4",
                "direct"
              ]
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "视频流",
            "content": {
              "video/mp4": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "format": "binary"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "206": {
            "description": "Range 请求部分内容"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/resources/{id}/subtitles": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "🔵 [新增] 获取字幕列表",
        "description": "获取与该视频资源关联的字幕文件（内置+外挂）。",
        "operationId": "listSubtitles",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "Player"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "视频资源 ID",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "字幕列表",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "type": "array",
                          "items": {
                            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Subtitle"
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/user/history": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "❌ [验证失败] 获取观看历史",
        "description": "性能优化中。",
        "operationId": "getHistory",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "failed_verification",
        "tags": [
          "User"
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "历史记录",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "post": {
        "summary": "🟠 [已开发未验证] 上报播放进度",
        "description": "上报播放进度心跳。",
        "operationId": "reportProgress",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "User"
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "resource_id",
                  "position_sec",
                  "total_duration",
                  "device_id"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "resource_id": {
                    "type": "string"
                  },
                  "position_sec": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "当前播放秒数"
                  },
                  "total_duration": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "视频总秒数 (必须由播放器提供)"
                  },
                  "device_id": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "设备唯一标识 (UUID)，用于多端续播区分"
                  },
                  "device_name": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "设备名称 (可选)"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "上报成功"
          }
        }
      },
      "delete": {
        "summary": "🔵 [新增] 清空观看历史",
        "description": "清空当前用户的所有观看历史记录。",
        "operationId": "clearAllHistory",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "User"
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "清空成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/user/history/{resource_id}": {
      "delete": {
        "summary": "🔵 [新增] 删除单条历史记录",
        "description": "删除指定资源（电影/剧集单集）的观看记录。",
        "operationId": "deleteHistoryItem",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "User"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "resource_id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "要删除的资源 ID",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "删除成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "404": {
            "description": "记录不存在"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/storage/sources": {
      "get": {
        "summary": "✅ [验证通过] 获取存储源列表",
        "description": "列出所有已配置的存储源。",
        "operationId": "listStorageSources",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "stable",
        "tags": [
          "Storage"
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "存储源列表",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "type": "array",
                          "items": {
                            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/StorageSource"
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "post": {
        "summary": "🟠 [已开发未验证] 添加存储源",
        "description": "添加新的媒体库来源。",
        "operationId": "addStorageSource",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "Storage"
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/StorageSourceRequest"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "添加成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ApiResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/v1/storage/sources/{id}": {
      "delete": {
        "summary": "🟠 [已开发未验证] 删除存储源",
        "description": "移除指定的存储源配置。",
        "operationId": "deleteStorageSource",
        "x-lifecycle-status": "implemented_unverified",
        "tags": [
          "Storage"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "存储源 ID",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "keep_metadata",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "是否保留元数据。",
            "schema": {
              "type": "boolean",
              "default": false
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "删除成功",
